# Ignore patterns for `tauri dev`'s file watcher — gui/src-tauri scope.
#
# IMPORTANT: this Tauri version roots each `.taurignore` at the file's
# OWN parent directory, so the patterns here only govern paths under
# `gui/src-tauri/`. Workspace-level ignores (plugins-ext/, IronRDP/, the
# repo-root target dirs) MUST live in the repo-root `.taurignore` — see
# ../../.taurignore — because the GUI's path dep on the repo-root crate
# makes the repo root a separate watch folder that this file can't reach.
#
# macOS Finder writes `.DS_Store` whenever a folder is accessed, which
# the watcher would treat as a source-change → rebuild loop; exclude it
# and local build/editor cruft under this crate.

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Build artefacts under this crate (target/, target-plugin-pack/).
target/
**/target/
target-plugin-pack/

# Generated dist tree
dist/
